summary: Dogfrog by Matt Furie - Dogfrog is one of 1,000 Hedz. Drawn by Matt Furie in 2022. The overall design combines elements of both a dog and a frog, reflecting its unique origin. A large, expressive face with wide, brown eyes that convey a sense of curiosity and joy. An orange face and long floppy ears, reminiscent of a dog.
